{"tid":504638,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"京老虎咬死人案開庭 家屬索償$257萬","createTime":"2017-12-20T08:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T11:49:26.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28a4b56682ae61a370db90e24e483141eddf8110","tid":504638,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>京老虎咬死人案開庭 家屬索償$257萬</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1970000/1974246/20JCA005__20171220_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1970000%2F1974246%2F20JCA005__20171220_L.jpg&h=e5c3e3b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">北京八達嶺野生動物園，去年發生東北虎咬死遊客事件。（法新社資料圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n北京八達嶺野生動物園去年發生東北虎咬死遊客事件，死者家屬向動物園索賠一案，昨在北京延慶區法院開庭。事主律師認為，動物園要為事件負70%責任，索償增至218萬元人民幣（約257萬港元），法庭會擇日宣判。<br />\n<br />\n事發在去年7月，事主趙女士一家三口在動物園自駕遊，趙女士與其母在猛獸區先後下車，被老虎襲擊。趙女士受傷，其母身亡，事件引發廣泛關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1974246/%E4%BA%AC%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E%E5%92%AC%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E6%A1%88%E9%96%8B%E5%BA%AD%20%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F$257%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1974246%2F%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%2599%258E%25E5%2592%25AC%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25BA%25AD%2520%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F%24257%25E8%2590%25AC&d=UxwceqvxZF8HMDpdtcTRI7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=9e02eb01\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1974246/%E4%BA%AC%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E%E5%92%AC%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E6%A1%88%E9%96%8B%E5%BA%AD%20%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F$257%E8%90%AC</a>"},{"pid":"aac3ba4cb8e4ddeea2247d8982cb808a79ce4369","tid":504638,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T08:36:01.000Z","msg":"Fat fat la"},{"pid":"